{"tid":1805296,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普首度成為美國國民最崇拜人物","createTime":"2019-12-31T14:19:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T14:42:43.000Z","uid":125193,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dda0fae04c23bcf696dc9cb94e6ea4028d97e213","tid":1805296,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T14:19:52.000Z","msg":"民調機構蓋洛普最新調查顯示，美國總統特朗普，及前任總統奧巴馬，雙雙成為2019年度，最受美國國民崇拜的人物。<br />\n<br />\n今次是特朗普首度成為國民最崇拜人物，奧巴馬就是第12次，兩人在這項年度調查中，都獲得18%國民認定是目前全球各地在生人士中，最受敬重的男性。<br />\n<br />\n支持特朗普的受訪者中，45%都是共和黨員，支持奧巴馬的人中，就有41%受訪者屬於民主黨。<br />\n<br />\n除了特朗普及奧巴馬外，其餘在前十名內的最受崇拜人物，支持率都不足2%，這些人物包括前總統卡特、微軟創辦人蓋茨、教宗方濟各、加州眾議員希夫、資深參議員桑德斯、股神巴菲特及達賴喇嘛等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500240-20191231.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500240-20191231.htm&d=WJuKoENqNSNgO%2FFXDb0as99AtAt3lYzSqFOpIRNeugk%3D&h=74efa916\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500240-20191231.htm&h=73ee12bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500240-20191231.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9a033e9112ddc803e39d9e41fed347acfbdbb2e5","tid":1805296,"uid":293677,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T14:23:04.000Z","msg":"奧巴馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死左膠<br />\n方濟各<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />奶共狗<br />\n侵侵 我偶像<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"124ba422a1a2b7be411ac4358ad877016f6b47c2","tid":1805296,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a033e9112ddc803e39d9e41fed347acfbdbb2e5","tid":1805296,"uid":293677,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T14:23:04.000Z","msg":"奧巴馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死左膠<br />\n方濟各<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj